@startuml
title MediZano - Tiempo de devoluciones
robust "Solicitud" as Sol
robust "Validacion" as Val
robust "Autorizacion" as Aut
robust "Inventario" as Inv
robust "Nota de credito" as Nota
@0
Sol is Recibida
Val is Pendiente
Aut is Pendiente
Inv is SinCambios
Nota is Pendiente
@5
Sol is EnProceso
Val is Revisando
@10
Val is Conforme
Aut is Evaluando
@15
Aut is Aprobada
Inv is Reintegrando
Nota is Generando
@20
Sol is Finalizada
Inv is Actualizado
Nota is Emitida
@enduml
